Launching on 8 August, the line will be carried in 700 stores globally, as well as online.

The line features kimono, wrap-tie and pleated dresses in patterns and block colours.

There are also plenty of wrap-tie blouses in a range of vibrant colours, chunky knits for winter, as well as range of jewellery and accessories.

