The brand, which was already a huge success at London Fashion Week and in certain social circles, went global when Kate wore her £500 Issa wrap dress for her engagement announcement in 2010.

It sparked one of the first of many 'Kate Middleton fashion frenzies' and put the label even more firmly on the style map.

